# Component Layer Rules

## Naming
- PascalCase: `UserProfile.tsx`
- Folder grouping for complex components

## Pattern
```tsx
interface Props {
  user: User;
  onUpdate?: (user: User) => void;
}

export function UserProfile({ user, onUpdate }: Props) {
  return (
    <div className="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 p-6">
      {/* content */}
    </div>
  );
}
```

## UI Standards (Dark Theme)
```
Background: gray-950
Cards: gray-900
Inputs: gray-800
Borders: gray-700
Text: white / gray-400
Accent: red-500 (brand)
```

## Component Categories
- `/components/ui/` - Base UI (Button, Input, Card)
- `/components/forms/` - Form components
- `/components/layout/` - Navigation, Footer
- `/components/` - Feature-specific
